question: Which restaurant is on the path towards Friedman Benda Gallery, New York, NY within a 60 kilometers radius from Country Inn & Suites by Carlson, NY?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.938488 40.753067)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.003515 40.750103)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.938488 40.753067)',4326)::geography, 60000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.938488 40.753067)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
